list.t:
set the first three bits of the
          DSCP field to 0b000 (reset the 3 bits of the former ToS Precedence
          field, defined in  , and clarified in );

set the first three bits of the
          DSCP field to 0b000 (reset the 3 bits of the former ToS Precedence
          field), unless the first two bits of the DSCP field are 0b11;

set the first three bits of the DSCP field
          to any value different than 0b000 (replace the 3 bits of the former
          ToS Precedence field);

set the last three bits of the DSCP
          field to 0b000, unless the first two bits of the DSCP field are
          0b11;

